headline: Three Reasons Why FFIV is Risky and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: The past six months have been a windfall for F5’s shareholders. The company’s stock price has jumped 50.5%, hitting $257.62 per share. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
